name: Birthday Cake
description: Celebrate your birthday everyday, with our delicious vanilla cake flavored confection. The Birthday Cake Macaron is served with a healthy dose of edible glitter and tie-dye shell, what's not to love?

name: Chocolate Molten
description: The Chocolate Molten Macaron has a milk chocolate shell filled with dark chocolate ganache and a rich molten center!

name: Cookie Dough
description: Who says you can't eat cookie dough? The Cookie Dough Macaron has all the buttery goodness of your favorite cookie with mini chocolate chips.

name: Fruity Cereal
description: Our Fruity Cereal Macaron is your childhood treat all grown up. Enjoy the sweetness of the fruity flavor without the sugar overload.

name: Peanut Butter & Jelly
description: You'll go nuts for the Peanut Butter & Jelly Macaron, with an all-natural, creamy peanut butter filling and a grape jelly surprise in the center.

name: Raspberry Jam
description: With its delicious raspberry center and powdered sugar shell you won't be able to resist what is possibly our new favorite flavor... Raspberry 'Jam'! Dairy Free*

name: Red Velvet
description: With its lush red shell and savory cream cheese filling, this Red Velvet Macaron is certain to steal the show.

name: Strawberry Shortcake
description: Perfectly pink shells filled with a light buttercream and a strawberry fruit compote center. The Strawberry Shortcake Macaron is a classic.
